
= co-organizer of [[Open Science Summit]]

=Bio=

"Khadijah M. Britton, JD is a passionate advocate for open science in the public interest. As founder and CEO of BetterBio, a nonprofit news organization dedicated to empowering disenfranchised communities with information they need to lead healthy and successful lives, she teaches low-income communities of color the research and critical thinking skills to excel in our technology and life-science driven economy. She contributes critical examination of science research and communications to mainstream publications including Scientific American Blogs and the Boston Phoenix."


